    "en": {
      "title": "A person is shot and killed after entering a house in Ratmalana",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that two persons entered a house in Silva Mawatha area, Ratmalana and shot a person in the house with a firearm and fled.",
        "The person who was seriously injured by the gunshot died after being admitted to the Kalubowila hospital.",
        "A 30-year-old man has died and a T.56 firearm has been used for the shooting. The cause of the murder has not been ascertained and the body has been deposited in Kalubowila Hospital."
      ],
